abstract: The sales could free JPMorgan, Capital One and TCF Financial from the government’s bailout restrictions.
snippet: The sales could free JPMorgan, Capital One and TCF Financial from the government’s bailout restrictions.
lead_paragraph: A year after the federal government rescued the nation’s financial industry, the Treasury Department announced Thursday that it would auction off its remaining investments in three large banks, freeing the lenders from the federal bailout program.

headline.main: Treasury to Auction Off Big-Bank Warrants
headline.print_headline: Treasury to Auction Off Big-Bank Warrants

abstract: Despite JPMorgan Chase‘s generous and carefully constructed deal to buy the rest of Cazenove, it may not be able to preserve the historic firm’s legacy, Breakingviews says.
snippet: Despite JPMorgan Chase‘s generous and carefully constructed deal to buy the rest of Cazenove, it may not be able to preserve the historic firm’s legacy, Breakingviews says.
lead_paragraph: After 185 years on its own and five in shared accommodations, Cazenove, the British stockbroker, is moving into the House of Morgan.
